---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const effectiveDate = 'June 13, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Averde AI collects, uses, and protects the information you share through this site."
>
  <section class="bg-green-deep py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-cream leading-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-cream/70 text-lg">How I handle the information you share with this site.</p>
      <p class="text-cream/50 text-sm mt-3">Last updated: {effectiveDate}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 prose prose-lg prose-headings:text-green-deep prose-headings:font-bold prose-a:text-green-mid prose-p:text-dark prose-li:text-dark max-w-none">

      <p>
        Averde AI is a solo consultancy run by Mark Bloomfield, based in Boulder, Colorado, working with
        clients nationwide. This page explains what information I collect through
        <a href="https://averde.ai">averde.ai</a>, why, and what I do with it. If anything here is unclear,
        email <a href="mailto:mark@averde.ai">mark@averde.ai</a> and I'll answer plainly.
      </p>

      <h2>What I collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Information you give me.</strong> When you run the free Website Audit, send a message
        through the contact form, or request a download, you share your email address, your website URL, and
        any details you type into the form.</li>
        <li><strong>Basic usage data.</strong> If analytics is enabled, I collect aggregate, non-identifying
        information about how pages are used (which pages get visited, roughly where visitors come from). I use
        this to understand what's useful, not to track individuals.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How I use it</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To run your audit and send you the report.</li>
        <li>To reply to your message or follow up about working together.</li>
        <li>To send you something you specifically asked for (like a download).</li>
        <li>To improve the site and the services I offer.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>I don't sell your information, rent it, or share it for anyone else's advertising.</p>

      <h2>Who I share it with</h2>
      <p>
        I use a small set of trusted services to run the site. Your information passes through them only so they
        can do their job:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — stores audit and form submissions.</li>
        <li><strong>Resend</strong> — sends the emails I reply with.</li>
        <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — hosts the site.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — aggregate usage measurement, if enabled (uses cookies).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        The site itself doesn't need cookies to work. If analytics is enabled, the analytics provider may set
        cookies to measure usage. You can block or delete cookies in your browser settings without breaking the
        site.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        You can ask me to show you what I have, correct it, or delete it. Email
        <a href="mailto:mark@averde.ai">mark@averde.ai</a> and I'll take care of it. You can also unsubscribe from
        any email I send at any time.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        I keep audit and inquiry records only as long as they're useful for following up or doing the work, then
        I remove them. If you ask me to delete your information sooner, I will.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>
        If I change how I handle data, I'll update this page and the date at the top.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about privacy? Email <a href="mailto:mark@averde.ai">mark@averde.ai</a>.
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
